<plot>On her journey to peel away the layers to uncover the reasons why people still bleach their skin, filmmaker Dami Akinnusi meets with experts in the field of Dermatology, Psychiatry and Cultural history. As she follows a young woman lightening her skin, she asks why in the 21st century their is still a negative attitude towards darker skin.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?074425</url></doc>
